Package com.ss4group8

Class Group

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ss4group8.Group
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    LabGroup, LectureGroup, TutorialGroup
    public class Group
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents study groups (LectureGroup, TutorialGroup and LabGroup) for a course. A course must have at least one lecture group. A course can have many or no tutorial groups and lab groups. Student enrolled in this course must also be enrolled in one of the groups of each type.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Ma Xiao, Fu Mengyan, Kevin Steven Kihata, Ng Chen Ee Kenneth, Ian Tan Yi
